# Fake Product Detection using Blockchain & Machine Learning

## Overview
This project identifies counterfeit products using machine learning and blockchain verification.

## Architecture
- Android App (User Interface)
- Backend API (ML model)
- Blockchain (Product validation)

## Features
- Product authenticity check
- QR/ID verification
- ML classification
- Blockchain integration

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask / FastAPI
- Android (Java/Kotlin)
- Blockchain

## Project Structure
app/        -> Android Application  
backend/    -> ML and API  
docs/       -> Documentation  

## How to Run

### Backend
pip install -r requirements.txt  
python app.py  

### Android
Open in Android Studio

